Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Mari?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.15,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had sworn to myself that I would never speak that way in front of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think that was precisely what made you remember me, Raku-sama...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather ironic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to come back to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.67,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually did make friends with a girl who talked like that, many years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sure she was frail too.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.05,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, our first meeting was during that summer ten years ago, Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That summer ten years ago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.98,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That makes you the same as Onodera and Chitoge...
