Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.50,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first meeting was during that summer ten years ago, Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was very frail when I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.84,0:01:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my father brought me to a sanatorium in the mountains, where the air was fresh and clean.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.09,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was another day of boredom for me in my hospital room.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'd always been so delicate,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never quite had the chance play outside with other children.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.12,0:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So your name's Marika, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.11,0:01:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my daddy always calls me "Mari" anyhow.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Anyhow"? "Mari" it is, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.99,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you heard that, you started coming to my room every day,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.48,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.69,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,bringing me back little things you'd found on the mountain, as souvenirs, and showed me such a good time.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right. I do remember doing that, years ago!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kindness made me so happy, Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one day, my father asked me...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.23,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, have you taken a fancy to that young'n?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say so, an' I'll make him marry you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.71,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Rakkun.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Rakkun, what kinda girls do ya like?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Girls?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I dunno.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, girly girls, I guess?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, ones with long hair and stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting that day, I went right to work!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the lessons and practice that I used to hate, I threw myself into them!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.12,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mastered the proper manner of \Nspeech and acquired an education!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.05,0:02:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was full speed ahead for me to become the ideal woman that you sought!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I did for so many years, just to meet you once more.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.91,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our promise was the one thing that kept me going.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for speaking as if you have an obligation to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... I wanted so desperately to convey how I feel.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We had that photo taken when we were about to part ways,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we would never forget our cherished promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She did it for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She loved me that much, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me, it hardly meant anything at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who knew it was so important to her?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, please don't feel so badly about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.28,0:03:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that wanting you to remember me was my own self-indulgence.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.86,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you don't have to force yourself to remember me anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh... no way!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna concentrate with every nerve in my body!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the gesture, but it's really all right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.62,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to take me in as you see me now: everything about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marika who became such a lovely girl for your sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to see that.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll flaunt myself to you, and I've made up my mind about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on in, I'm going to make sure you don't forget me!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, first things first...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Raku-sama, you have a grain of rice on your cheek!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,An unforgettable memory...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first one.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.41,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, Raku-sama. I'll see you at school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Miss Marika, what about your medicine?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it! I feel much better now!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met before, ten years ago?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.18,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, your father certainly said so.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you two were pretty close, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you remember anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why is your face so red? Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the moment that I first saw you,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I did get the feeling that we could be good friends, Chitoge-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why did you wait so long to tell us something so important?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is, I couldn't find the right time!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the keys in question?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.55,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never dreamed that you'd have a key like this, too, Kosaki-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here. I wonder what this means.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.88,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We all met Darling ten years ago, made some kind of promise, and now we all have keys.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, I only made the promise with one girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.72,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was that promise about in the first place?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember, no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you remember what the promise was about?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.76,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but of course, it could be none other than a promise of marriage!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just assumed it was the same for the rest of you, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the promise I made when I bade Raku-sama farewell.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he may not remember that!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.19,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, didn't you say you made such a promise when you said goodbye?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think she's the one?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, there's still a lot we don't know...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marriage?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.32,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it possible that I made such a bold promise with Ichijou-kun, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If... If I did...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it was some kind of important promise,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I never would've thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then why are there three keys?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth about this promise...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.20,0:06:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't want to tell us, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How about just a little hint?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't know myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were totally bragging about how you knew the answer!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes—no, I am very, very sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I am also astonished.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew that there were others apart from myself with keys.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the first I have heard of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I do recall that in our conversations,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you had mentioned another playmate of yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this "truth" of yours...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Needless to say...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.67,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was referring to how much I was in love with you when I made that promise!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.31,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know only what concerns my own promise, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.53,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means one of these keys is real, and the others aren't.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.69,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then we're stuck waiting until your locket is repaired, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.67,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, I am the one who shall wed Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we've already shared a kiss.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss? Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool us anymore. I know you're just saying that to—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait—you two kissed?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.01,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! No, no! It was so sudden! I had no way of resisting!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you did kiss! Lowlife scum! I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You filthy beast!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissing a girl you've just met.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it wasn't really a kiss! Her lips just touched my cheek, that's all!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.96,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, considering who's more appropriate for Raku-sama, it's only natural, I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well! You're one to talk, after making a move on {\i1}my{\i0} darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You thieving cat.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least cats are more endearing than gorillas.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more suitable for Darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose side are you on, Kosaki-chan?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.00,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Onodera-sama?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um... Well, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, before you answer...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, how do you feel about Raku-sama?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.73,0:08:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're thinking that you might have promised to marry him years ago,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and possibly that you and he—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.55,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that I might have made such a promise years ago,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but for now I think of him as a good friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? In that case, let's be friends!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Kosaki-chan is my friend!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good "friend," huh? Well, that's a bummer.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, now, why so uptight? You certainly are a stingy gorilla.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Ichijou-kun and I did meet in the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, that makes him my first love.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kosaki-chan doesn't need a thieving cat like you for a friend!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if Ichijou-kun loves Chitoge-chan?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, my! What a loud voice you have, Gorilla!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, man, you make my blood boil! What's so funny?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of those girls is the one I made the promise with?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What a barbaric gorilla you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the one I love now is Onodera.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.94,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feelings right now and my feelings from the past, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is all but settled that my key is the genuine one.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku-sama and I are bound by the red thread of destiny—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? So why didn't he remember a thing about you, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you gimme that hogwash, now!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.37,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Raku-sama, will you be so kind as to meet my father tomorrow?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you need to come by at least once to pay your respects.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have to decide on the date of our engagement.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you trying to get at?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I make it clear that I had no clue that I had a fiancée?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.61,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am well aware of that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.38,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that doesn't mean that our engagement has been annulled.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.70,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, we just might see the good in each other for the first time once we've become husband and wife!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even old enough to get married yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.00,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Tachibana-san, do you not think that you're being rather shameless?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of his girlfriend, even!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, forgive me for being so remiss, Kirisaki-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always being so kind to my husband.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling your husband?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He never even acknowledged the engagement in the first place, did he now?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's invalid!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is no obstacle.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.10,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents have been arranging engagements for their children since time immemorial.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that upsets you, you'll have to take it up with my father.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what choice do I have?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she steamrolled over me, I can't ditch now.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.81,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you haven't given up being an indecisive bean sprout!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you expect me to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go ahead and show up at her house,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to come back with a wedding date all settled.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that, lately your acting could fool even me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like you're possessed or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.76,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that if my people found out that you had a fiancée...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not doing it for myself, but if {\i1}they{\i0} were to find out...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.03,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? If he finds out, who knows what that Four Eyes will do to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.54,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen up. You're gonna stand up to her father and have him call off the engagement, all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like it's gonna be that simple.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then, Raku-sama, welcome to my home!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.01,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire top floor of this building is my home.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The entire floor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.44,0:12:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Tachibana...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, did you call me Tachibana?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.67,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to call me Marika!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guy is your dad, Tachibana?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.70,0:12:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he was the police commissioner, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's probably pretty scary, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, far from it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is a very kind man!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.92,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He even calls me "Mari," and he's constantly worrying about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you'll like him, too, Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, home already, Mari?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, Father! I was just about to summon you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa, scary! Her old man's face is so scary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a second there, I thought he was a yakuza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, he's even more imposing than any yakuza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.81,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! This young man is my fiancé, Ichijou Raku-sama.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he gorgeous?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Um... It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, I... Sorry, I mean I...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.63,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're Ichijou's son, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're starting to take after your old man, I'd say.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have a seat.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a nice, long chat. Is your old man doing all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See this scar?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um, it looks really cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you injured on the job?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a badge of honor?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.53,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your old man gave me this scar many years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're the spitting image of your father, looking at you
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is making it throb all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell were you thinking, Dad?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.04,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that was also the day we acknowledged each other's power.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have been on different sides,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but we did bond enough to drink together, man-to-man.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.30,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But to this day, my dream is to toss that bastard behind bars!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Scary! This old man is beyond scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's way more like a yakuza than any of our guys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.73,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way in hell I have the balls to tell him to call off the engagement!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's set aside such trivial matters for now.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.06,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Time certainly flies! My Marika is old enough to get married now, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.56,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you've cared deeply for her all this time yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I—
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku-sama tells me that he had forgotten all about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You plumb forgot?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.92,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What in blue blazes are you sayin'?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.40,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You were never told about this engagement, is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that scumbag...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he treat a promise between two men so lightly!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.77,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I see him, I'll make him pay in full!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, there's one thing that bothers me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.13,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you're not in love with another girl right now, are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.05,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come callin' here when you done got yourself a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, please calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't the one to blame here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite everything, I'm fine with the situation.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.14,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made up my mind to steal him from his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.73,0:15:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I would not be worthy of being joined with him in marriage.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, then I have no objection.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you always close to my daughter like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, this is just... Marika's one-sided—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rest assured!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our relationship is nothing but honorable and virtuous—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Look at you, Raku-sama! There's no need to be embarrassed!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we've shared our first kiss already.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, do you have to go blurting out—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you... Don't you reckon you should be gettin' into that stuff
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,after you've gotten to know each other a lil' more? Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.64,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, this won't do. To think that I haven't even offered you tea yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back with it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her timing's awful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Hey, come back here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't leave me alone, please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, crap, what am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is beyond bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to find a way out of this!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've gotta think of a good excuse.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... my Marika...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From time to time, even though it's years later,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll still boast about what you were like back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, something like this happened, or we talked about such-and-such...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The most trivial things, even now.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All that clutter you left behind in her hospital room back then,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.77,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,she still treasures it all to this day.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She still talks like that about what happend back then?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on in, I'm going to make sure you don't forget me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it does seem to make her happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Marika-san's dad, but right now...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, there's someone else that I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not Marika-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I dislike Marika-san,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.04,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've cared for that girl for so long.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.37,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm really, really sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.66,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. So you finally done gone an' spit it out, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.65,0:18:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a young'un, so it's not something you can just be practical about.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no need to beat around the bush like that right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that girl, is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, actually, you see...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.76,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she then? What are you, a philanderer?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not, I'm not, I swear I'm not!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just really complicated, all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, what the hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But a promise is a promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you're gonna make my daughter happy, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep that in mind, boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari is quite a handful, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.22,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, man. I wonder if I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your conversation with my father?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great dad, all right.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I could sense just how precious you are to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a little scary, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you seem to have hit it off!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, someday he might become your father too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It never ceases to amaze me how pushy you can be.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta tell you, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you carry it so far?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.69,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my! Do I really need to spell it out for you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in this world becomes yours if you do not move to acquire it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with romance—your only hope is to be aggressive.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.10,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like she's talking about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is to make an effort to express my feelings,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and make an effort to change myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.27,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku-sama! Please enlighten me again.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.42,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of girl do you prefer now?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.86,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I can transform myself in any way, as long as it's for your sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say I have a preference.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.17,0:19:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're cute enough the way you are now, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you've put in all this effort for me
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me happy, and I think you're an amazing girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something that just anyone can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, whether your hair is long or short,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you talk like you do now, or like you did back then,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,either way, I think you're a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.83,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Springing something like that on me out of nowhere... Now I'm in a pickle!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Um! D-Don't look this way, ya hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look this way!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on! It's like you've turned into a different person now!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you embarrassed, by any chance?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't embarrassed by a long shot!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay away from me, ya hear?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Raku-sama was forward with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Forward?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation did you go and do to my daughter?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that your tenth one?
